ai_summary.Response: This commit updates the SAML configuration details for the PageDNA SaaS application within Microsoft Entra documentation. Specifically, it modifies the `Identifier` and `Reply URL` values to include `/clients/` in the URL for the `www.nationsprint.com` domain. Additionally, the `Sign on URL` for `www.nationsprint.com` has also been updated to reflect this change.
